\c 8
\s Vana vaBhenjamini naSauro
\p
\v 1 Zvino Bhenjamini wakabereka Bhera dangwe rake, Ashibheri wepiri\x + 7.6. Gen.. 46.21. Num.. 26.38.\x*, naAhara wetatu\x + 7.12.\x*,
\v 2 Noha wechina, naRafa weshanu.
\v 3 Uye Bhera waiva nevanakomana: Adhari, naGera, naAbhihudhi\x + Num.. 26.40.\x*,
\v 4 naAbhishuwa, naNaamani\x + Num.. 26.40.\x*, naAhowa\x + 2 Sam. 23.28.\x*,
\v 5 naGera, naShefufani, naHuramu.
\v 6 Zvino ava vanakomana vaEhudhi: Ndivo misoro yemadzibaba evagari vepaGebha\x + Josh. 18.24.\x*, uye vakavatapira kuManahati\x + 2.52,54.\x*;
\v 7 naNaamani\x + 8.4,5.\x*, naAhiya\x + 8.4,5.\x*, naGera\x + 8.4,5.\x*, iye wakavatapa; ndokubereka Uza naAhihudhi.
\v 8 Shaharaimu ndokubereka panyika yaMoabhu, shure kwekuvadzinga kwake. Hushimi naBhahara vaiva vakadzi vake.
\v 9 Zvino wakabereka kumukadzi wake Hodheshi: Jobhabhu, naZibhia, naMesha, naMarikamu,
\v 10 naJeuzi, naSakiya, naMirima. Ava vanakomana vake, misoro yemadzibaba.
\v 11 Zvino kuna Hushimi wakabereka Abhitubhi naEripahari.
\v 12 Uye vanakomana vaEripahari: Ebheri, naMishamu, naShemedhi; iye wakavaka Ono\x + Ezi. 2.33. Neh. 7.37. 11.35.\x*\x + Neh. 6.2.\x*, neRodhi, nemisha yawo\x + Neh. 6.2.\x*\x + Ezi. 2.33. Neh. 7.37. 11.35.\x*\x + Mab. 9.32,35,38.\x*,
\v 13 naBheriya, naShema\x + 8.21.\x*; ivo vaiva misoro yemadzibaba kuvagari vepaAjaroni\x + Josh. 10.12. Josh. 19.42.\x*; ivo vaiva vadzinga vagari vepaGati\x + 1 Sam. 17.4.\x*;
\v 14 naAhiyo, Shashaki, naJeremoti,
\v 15 naZebhadhia, naAradhi, naEdheri,
\v 16 naMikayeri, naIshipa, naJoha, vanakomana vaBheriya\x + 8.13.\x*;
\v 17 naZebhadhia, naMeshuramu, naHiziki, naHebheri,
\v 18 naIshimerai, naIziriya, naJobhabhu, vanakomana vaEripahari\x + 8.12.\x*;
\v 19 naJakimu, naZikiri, naZabhudhi,
\v 20 naErienai, naZiretai, naEriyeri,
\v 21 naAdhaya, naBheraya, naShimurati, vanakomana vaShimei;
\v 22 naIshipani, naEbheri, naEriyeri,
\v 23 naAbhudhoni, naZikiri, naHanani,
\v 24 naHananiya, naEramu, naAnitotiya,
\v 25 naIfudheya, naPenueri, vanakomana vaShashaki\x + 8.14.\x*;
\v 26 naShamusherai, naShehariya, naAtariya,
\v 27 naJaareshiya, naEriya, naZikiri, vanakomana vaJerohamu.
\v 28 Ava vaiva misoro yemadzibaba, misoro pamadzinza avo; ava vaigara muJerusarema.
\p
\v 29 NepaGibhiyoni\x + 9.35-38.\x* paigara baba vaGibhiyoni; nezita remukadzi wake raiva Mahaka\x + Josh. 9.3.\x*;
\v 30 uye mwanakomana wake dangwe aiva Abhidhoni; naZuri, naKishi, naBhahari, naNadhabhi,
\v 31 naGedhori, naAhiyo, naZekeri.
\v 32 Mikiroti ndokubereka Shimeya\x + 9.37.\x*. Uye avawo vaigara pakatarisana nehama dzavo muJerusarema, pamwe nehama dzavo.
\p
\v 33 Neri\x + 9.39-44.\x* ndokubereka Kishi, Kishi ndokubereka Sauro, Sauro ndokubereka Jonatani, naMariki-Shua\x + 1 Sam. 9.1. 14.51.\x*, naAbhinadhabhu, naEshibhaari\x + 10.2. 1 Sam. 31.2.\x*.
\v 34 Zvino mwanakomana waJonatani waiva Meribhi-Bhaari; Meribhi-Bhaari ndokubereka Mika\x + 2 Sam. 9.12.\x*.
\v 35 Nevanakomana vaMika: Pitoni, naMereki, naTareya, naAhazi.
\v 36 Ahazi ndokubereka Jehoadha, Jehoadha ndokubereka Aremeti, naAzimavheti, naZimiri; Zimiri ndokubereka Moza;
\v 37 Moza ndokubereka Bhineya; Rafa waiva mwanakomana wake, Ereasa mwanakomana wake, Azeri mwanakomana wake.
\v 38 Zvino Azeri waiva nevanakomana vatanhatu; uye awa ndiwo mazita avo: Azirikamu, Bhokeru, naIshimaeri, naShearia, naObhadhiya, naHanani. Ava vese vaiva vanakomana vaAzeri.
\v 39 Nevanakomana vaEsheki munin'ina wake: Uramu dangwe rake, Jeushi wepiri, naErifereti wetatu.
\v 40 Zvino vanakomana vaUramu vaiva varume vane simba veumhare, vaihwembura uta; vaiva nevanakomana vazhinji, nevanakomana vevanakomana, zana nemakumi mashanu. Ava vese vaiva vevanakomana vaBhenjamini\x + 5.18.\x*.